      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MYSTERY NELL (7) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (23.12) at Warragul. Form here at the trip excellent including two wins. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Can discover winning form. BE A SECRET (8) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at this track over 350m behind Cumulate (19.74) in a Mix 6/7. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Should be in this for a long way. ZAWADI (1) steps out for the first time at this course. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 3.5 lengths (24.69) at Traralgon. Expected to give a good account. ESPECIAL KIANI (4) is building a nice sequence of placings – must be respected.",
